metadata.name: OVERLU GENESIS MEGA LU#0002
metadata.description: OVERLU NFT is a dynamic upgradeable NFT asset. Owners can customize their unique appearances, meanwhile, unlock the corresponding premium utilities when upgrading appearance components or expanding slots of Avatars. GENESIS MEGA LU is the first product of the MGEA LU series and it is a standalone NFT asset, the owner of this rare asset also has the highest eligibility in the OVERLU ecosystem.
